=== Basic Named Captures ===
abc ~ (?<x>a)bc	(states = 6, threads = 1)	Matched! [1 captures]
  x: a[0-1] 
abc ~ a(?<x>b)c	(states = 6, threads = 1)	Matched! [1 captures]
  x: b[1-2] 
abc ~ ab(?<x>c)	(states = 6, threads = 1)	Matched! [1 captures]
  x: c[2-3] 
abc ~ (?<x>abc)	(states = 6, threads = 1)	Matched! [1 captures]
  x: abc[0-3] 

=== Multiple Captures ===
abc ~ (?<x>a)(?<y>b)(?<z>c)	(states = 10, threads = 1)	Matched! [3 captures]
  x: a[0-1] 
  y: b[1-2] 
  z: c[2-3] 
hello ~ (?<greeting>hello)	(states = 8, threads = 1)	Matched! [1 captures]
  greeting: hello[0-5] 
ab ~ (?<first>a)(?<second>b)	(states = 7, threads = 1)	Matched! [2 captures]
  first: a[0-1] 
  second: b[1-2] 

=== Captures with Star ===
 ~ (?<x>a)*	(states = 5, threads = 2)	Matched! [1 captures]
  x: []
aaa ~ (?<x>a)*	(states = 5, threads = 5)	Matched! [1 captures]
  x: [a[0-1] , a[1-2] , a[2-3] ]
aaabbb ~ (?<a>a)*(?<b>b)*	(states = 9, threads = 12)	Matched! [2 captures]
  a: [a[0-1] , a[1-2] , a[2-3] ]
  b: [b[3-4] , b[4-5] , b[5-6] ]

=== Captures with Optional ===
ac ~ a(?<x>b)?c	(states = 8, threads = 2)	Matched! [1 captures]
  x: None
abc ~ a(?<x>b)?c	(states = 8, threads = 2)	Matched! [1 captures]
  x: Some(b[1-2] )

=== Nested Captures ===
ab ~ (?<outer>(?<inner>a)b)	(states = 7, threads = 1)	Matched! [2 captures]
  inner: a[0-1] 
  outer: ab[0-2] 
abc ~ (?<x>a(?<y>b)c)	(states = 8, threads = 1)	Matched! [2 captures]
  x: abc[0-3] 
  y: b[1-2] 

=== Alternation with Captures ===
a ~ (?<x>a)|(?<y>b)	(states = 6, threads = 2)	Matched! [1 captures]
  x: a[0-1] 
b ~ (?<x>a)|(?<y>b)	(states = 6, threads = 2)	Matched! [1 captures]
  y: b[0-1] 

=== Complex Patterns ===
aba ~ (?<x>(?<y>a)(?<z>b))*	(states = 10, threads = 3)	No match
ababab ~ (?<pair>(?<a>a)(?<b>b))*	(states = 10, threads = 5)	Matched! [3 captures]
  a: [a[0-1] , a[2-3] , a[4-5] ]
  b: [b[1-2] , b[3-4] , b[5-6] ]
  pair: [ab[0-2] , ab[2-4] , ab[4-6] ]
